Downtown Southside Inbound

Description:

The Downtown Southside Inbound leaves the University Downtown Center and travels through Henry & State Streets in Downtown Binghamton, and Vestal Pkwy, Conklin Avenue, & Tompkins Street in Southside Binghamton, while also making stops at the BC Junction Bus Terminal and Mirabito Stadium enroute back to campus.

Operation Time:

Weekdays:
8:00 A.M. to 9:55 P.M.


Weekends:
11:30 A.M. to 6:15 P.M.
